ory-store-and-search/017-search-and-output-intelligence-implementation/004-confidence-calibration-labeled-set/assets/confidence-labeled-set.starter.json\",\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/017-search-and-output-intelligence-implementation/004-confidence-calibration-labeled-set/implementation-summary.md\",\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/017-search-and-output-intelligence-implementation/004-confidence-calibration-labeled-set/spec.md\"],\"findingsCount\":1,\"findingsSummary\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":1,\"P2\":0},\"findingsNew\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":1,\"P2\":0},\"findingDetails\":[{\"id\":\"F001\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"title\":\"Starter labeled-set file is not loadable by the shipped labeled-set loader\",\"dimension\":\"correctness\",\"category\":\"contract_safety\",\"file\":\".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/017-search-and-output-intelligence-implementation/004-confidence-calibration-labeled-set/assets/confidence-labeled-set.starter.json:1-5\",\"evidence\":\"loadLabeledSet() requires a top-level array and throws on objects, while fit-calibration.mjs documents the starter as {query,memoryId,relevant}[] but writes an object wrapper with pairs[]. Direct reproduction returned: labeled set must be a JSON array of {query, memoryId, relevant}.\",\"recommendation\":\"Either make confidence-labeled-set.starter.json a top-level pair array, or extend loadLabeledSet() to accept the documented metadata wrapper and validate its pairs array; add a regression that loads the shipped starter file.\",\"disposition\":\"active\",\"findingClass\":\"artifact-contract-mismatch\",\"scopeProof\":\"Direct reads of confidence-calibration.ts:73-76, fit-calibration.mjs:5-6 and 168-181, starter JSON:1-5, plus a read-only Node reproduction against the shipped artifact.\",\"affectedSurfaceHints\":[\"offline calibration follow-up\